column17: Hello:Because it is very important for us to hear your opinions we periodically ask for subscriber data and feedback. This information helps us land sponsors create new services to meet your needs and better our content. Your information will be coded and will remain confidential. If you have questions at any time about the survey or the procedures you may contact Isel Galvan at igalvan@smartbrief.com. Thank you very much for your time and support. Please start with the survey now by clicking on the Continue button below.P.S. BIO SmartBrief is 43000 readers strong -- spread the word!
